" Quicker switching between windows
nmap <silent> <C-h> <C-w>h
nmap <silent> <C-j> <C-w>j
nmap <silent> <C-k> <C-w>k
nmap <silent> <C-l> <C-w>l

" Navigate tabs
map <s-left> :tabp<CR>
map <s-right> :tabn<CR>

map <silent> <m-w> <c-w>+
map <silent> <m-k> <c-w>+

map <silent> <m-a> <c-w><
map <silent> <m-h> <c-w><

map <silent> <m-s> <c-w>-
map <silent> <m-j> <c-w>-

map <silent> <m-d> <c-w>>
map <silent> <m-l> <c-w>>

map <silent> <m-o> <c-o>:bd#<cr>
